Package com.intel.jndn.utils

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Client
    Base functionality provided by all NDN clients in this package.
    DynamicServer
    Defines the API for a Server producing Data packets dynamically; in other words, when an Interest arrives, this server will run a callback to determine what packet to send back.
    RepositoryServer
    Defines the API for a Server producing Data packets and storing them until they are requested; this server corresponds closely to use cases such as: cache, file system, web server.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InternalFace
    TODO waiting on Face to become overridable
    SegmentedClient
    Provide a client to simplify retrieving segmented Data packets over the NDN network.
    SegmentedServer
    Implementation of a RepositoryServer that segments packets stored in its repository.
    SimpleClient
    Provide a client to simplify information retrieval over the NDN network.
    SimpleServer
    Implementation of a DynamicServer that wraps the OnInterest callback with some encoding and pipeline support.
